# OPSEU Social Media Toolbox

## Stack
- Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4
- Static export (`output: 'export'`) — no backend in v1
- next-intl for EN/FR i18n with `[locale]` routing
- Zustand + localStorage for brand state
- html-to-image, JSZip, jsPDF for client-side exports

## Architecture
- All image processing is client-side only (privacy by design)
- Data access via `DataAdapter` interface — v1 uses `LocalStorageAdapter`
- Brand kit JSON schema version `1.0`
- CAAT OPSEU is the default division; brand colours in `src/lib/constants/brand.ts`

## Conventions
- Use `@/` import alias
- Client components marked `"use client"`
- Tool pages use `useUndoRedo` hook for edit history
- Member photo uploads require `ConsentModal` confirmation
- Colour pickers must show `ContrastChecker` warnings
- Commit at end of each milestone with conventional commits
- Update `docs/PROGRESS.md` after major work

## Testing
- Unit: Vitest in `src/**/*.test.ts`
- E2E/Smoke: Playwright in `e2e/` with `@smoke` tag
- Run `npm run test:unit` and `npm run test:smoke` after major changes
- axe-core a11y checks in Playwright smoke suite

## Do not
- Add backend APIs, analytics, or third-party tracking
- Use `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`
- Skip consent flow for member photo tools
- Commit secrets or `.env` files
